# Prefer the OS keychain instead of this file:
#
#   python3 credit_audit.py --store-gitlab-token
#
# That stores your git.drupalcode.org token encrypted in macOS Keychain
# (or the secret service on Linux with `keyring` installed). Input is
# hidden while you paste.
#
# Plaintext file fallback (not recommended):
#   cp .gitlab-token.example .gitlab-token
#   chmod 600 .gitlab-token
#
# .gitlab-token is gitignored — do not commit it.
